o process all 5 sources simultaneously.\" </example> <example>Context: User says \"process everything in .raw/ that hasn't been ingested yet\" assistant: \"I'll use wiki-ingest agents to handle each source in parallel.\" </example>\n","model":"sonnet","maxTurns":30,"tools":"Read, Write, Edit, Glob, Grep"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[61,67]],"key":"Progetto Sistemi WiKi/agents/wiki-ingest.md"},
